nodes.text: A skirmish took place at Moxonnic Manufacturing on Coruscant during the Clone Wars between misguided Jedi Master Ring-Sol Ambase and his Jedi Apprentice Nuru Kungurama.
Harro Kelpura appears in Ryder Windham's 2012 young readers novel, The Clone Wars: Secret Missions 4: Guardians of the Chiss Key.
